text.tspan: Share of population with mental or substance use disorders, males vs.
Share of males vs. females with any mental health or substance use disorder; this includes depression, anxiety, bipolar, eating
disorders, alcohol or drug use disorders, and schizophrenia. This share has been age-standardized assuming a constant age
structure to compare prevalence between countries and through time.
Source: IHME, Global Burden of Disease
